    I appreciate any advise my betters might give me.<br>
<br>
Teapray <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=d1c3b5><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub94.ezboard.com/bfirionavie.showLocalUserPublicProfile?login=adarion>Adarion</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br>  Posts: 27<br> <font color=#A62A2A>(6/8/02 11:10:37 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub94.ezboard.com/ffirionaviefrm9.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=435.topic&index=1>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: What Quests Recommened for Lowbies</span><hr size=1> The ghast hearts are one of the more painful parts of the TLC; I myself am a High Elf cleric who missed out on that.  I couldn't hunt them alone, as that terrible evil horse kept slaughtering me (not to mention the roaming brownies), and I couldn't convince any friends to join me in hunting Lesser Faydark for the ghasts.<br>
<br>
Now I am in my twentieth rank with the temple, and am unable to hunt ghast hearts for the temple quest any longer.  I may have to hire a younger adventurer to help me out with this.<br>
<br>
On another note...  your beloved is an OGRE?!<br>
<br>
*mutters something about what the world is coming to*<br>
<br>
